Name: test_get_post_schema_validation
Description:
Test: Validate the schema of the retrieved post data
    Purpose: Ensure the API response adheres to the expected schema (positive test)
    Expected Result: HTTP 200 OK, and response matches Pydantic model

Name: test_login_form_success
Description: UI Test: Validate successful login on practice test site

Name: test_login_form_failure
Description: UI Test: Validate failed login with incrorrect credentials

Name: test_update_post
Description: Skipped Test: Placeholder for future PUT request test

Name: test_get_post
Description:
Test: Retrieve a single post by ID
    Purpose: Validate the API returns correct post data for a valid ID (positive test)
    Expected Result: HTTP 200 OK, and response contains expected post fields

Name: test_create_post
Description:
Test: Create a new post via POST
    Purpose: Validate that the API successfully accepts new post data (positive test)
    Expected Result: HTTP 201 Created, and response includes submitted data

Name: test_post_not_found
Description:
Test: Attempt to retrieve a non-existent post
    Purpose: Validate the API correctly handles invalid post requests (negative test)
    Expected Result: HTTP 404 Not Found or empty response with HTTP 200 (JSONPlaceholder returns 200)

Name: test_homepage_title
Description: UI Test: Verify the page title of example.com

Name: test_delete_post
Description: Expected Failure Test: Attempt to delete a post (simulated)
